{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/story.png?t=1721679415\" /><br><strong>Sodden</strong> opens for you a dark thoughtful narrative of the game story of the survival horror genre. <br>Stylized 2D graphics emphasize only the silhouettes of the world around you. The elements of metroidvania will allow you to freely explore <strong>a closed science campus</strong>.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/storyhouse.gif ?t=1721679415\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/coop.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>You can survive in pairs thanks to the <u> local</u> cooperative. Build your tactics by working together.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/parkour.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>The complex architecture of the environment forces you to use the skills of <u>parkour</u>. You can avoid any collision with danger.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/monster.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>A large number of creepy creatures of different shapes and sizes will not leave you alone. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/diarymonster.gif?t=1721679415\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/weapon.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>A wide range of weapons will allow you to survive for a long time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/shelter.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>You can take a deep breath and plan your further actions in the scientific laboratory module. Cooking, water purification, item creation, safe sleep, charging a combat drone...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/cooking.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>Keep an eye on your health indicators: look for food and prepare it.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/coffeebreak.gif?t=1721679415\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/craft.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>Study the machine to create simple items or repair existing equipment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/looting.png?t=1721679415\" /><br>Look for the necessary materials on outings. Take as much as you can carry.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/extras/inventory.gif?t=1721679415\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721679415","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/page.bg.jpg?t=1721679415","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1721679415","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916980/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1721679415","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game may contain obscene text messages."},"demos":[{"appid":2999210,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea